Packages
com.guitariffic.controller This package defines all the controller classes for guitariffic.
com.guitariffic.controller.filter This package contains the filter support classes for guitariffic.
com.guitariffic.dao.chord This package controls all database access for the chord images.
com.guitariffic.dao.fakesheet This package defines all the loading and saving for the fake sheet to different file types.
com.guitariffic.dao.fakesheet.adapter This package contains all the file-specific adapters to load and save a fake sheet.
com.guitariffic.model This package defines all the model classes and data structures for guitariffic.
com.guitariffic.model.enums This package defines all the model class enums for guitariffic.
com.guitariffic.view This package defines all the view classes for guitariffic.
com.guitariffic.view.adapter This package defines the table adapters for the chord chart area.
